---

## ğŸ“¦ Installation

Install dependencies:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

## â–¶ï¸ Usage

Run the tool on any CSV:

```bash
python main.py yourfile.csv
```

Or skip saving the JSON report:

```bash
python main.py yourfile.csv --no-save
```

Reports will be generated in the `reports/` directory.

